    "Html": "<p>Change the bindings on the TextBlock/TextBox to {Binding Text,RelativeSource={RelativeSource Self},Converter={StaticResource TestConverter}}.</p>\r\n<p>The DataFieldBinding is always set to Explicit and can't be changed in order to control updates to the source. This is why Description would not update and thus why other bindings to Description would not update.</p>\r\n<p>Ben</p>\r\n",
